Please select the type of license you wish to search for.

NOTE: Some licenses are issued in the name of the business, not an individual. If you are searching for a business licensee (i.e., accountancy firms; architects and engineers certificates of authorization; barber shops; cemeteries; cosmetology and hairstyling shops; electrical contractor businesses; funeral homes; home improvement contractors; manicuring shops; pharmacies; public movers and warehousemen and skin care speciality shops) select Business Search below. Otherwise, select Person Search.

BUSINESS SEARCH PERSON SEARCH

Please Note: This website is intended to be used for VERIFICATION ONLY.
